Direct links to audio: Soundloud / Youtube

DJ Pohy comes correct with this 2 sided killer mix, printed in a very limited edition cassette tape, hand designed by Pohy himself: Only 3 copies in the world !

To get a chance to win the tape : head to our Instagram account & take part in the contest (ending January 6th 2022) : www.instagram.com/asymetrics/


The Asymetrics · DJ Pohy - Asymetrics Tape #1
